The '''Kessel run''' was an expression in [[Deal-slang]] that referred to the act of engaging in potentially dangerous deals or deals of such magnitude that they were risky or too hard to handle. The phrase referenced the dangerous [[Kessel Run/Legends|Kessel Run]] [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperlane]] many [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] used when smuggling [[Spice/Legends|spice]] from [[Kessel/Legends|Kessel]].

